00:25:59,200 --> 00:26:00,600
Švihák.

231
00:26:01,100 --> 00:26:02,670
Povedz mi úprimne,

232
00:26:02,770 --> 00:26:04,420
si šťastný, lebo ideš domov

233
00:26:04,450 --> 00:26:07,700
alebo kvôli týmto peniazom?
Prečo sa vôbec pýtaš?

234
00:26:07,900 --> 00:26:11,550
Nie je to tak, že by mal doma ženu a deti, takže
